text: Indian navy has foiled a piracy attempt on 5 Indian merchant vessels in international waters. Navy's frigate INS Sukanya intercepted 3 pirate ships and seized arms and ammunition from the pirates. News X has exclusive pictures of the anti - piracy operation. This operation was part of the International efforts to secure high seas ; India has been at the forefront of anti - piracy operations.
title: INS Sukanya intercepts pirate ships, arms seized.
